divs: sighting detailshello, my name is [cms\tg\pid] i, i live on the [pid] side of casa grande, around 9:20pm tonight i was in my front yard and looking in the direct of table top (west) and noticed two orange lights just to the north of table top. they would have been higher in the sky than table top is. they where at the same level with each other and did not move, side to side or up and down. the one close to table top went out the other stayed on. they did have a little flicker to them. about five minutes later the last one went out. they could hve been flares but the stayed at the same level all the time. this was the same location that my wife and i seen lights the night of the phoenix lights bakc in the 90s.
